***************************************************************************
* All modules under slib context are system space and can have their ******
* initial values in ukrnl.json file, final users just have to used to use *
* lib context, don't use slib context for your own modules. ***************
***************************************************************************

NOTE FOR DEVELOPERS:

Processes and Init folders have C examples of how to use low-level coding
for ukrnl.js. This coding space _slib_ has to be optional, and each module
would activate via the ukrnl.json configuration file.
